Environment
-----------
Start the environment:

cd ~/Digi/DigiEL-5.2/workspace/meconfig-ipv6-slip-jffs2/build/coretemplate/
. ./DigiEL.sh

tunslip6
--------
cd ~/Digi/DigiEL-5.2/workspace/meconfig-ipv6-slip-jffs2/build/coretemplate/contiki-2.x-20110606/tools
arm-linux-gcc tunslip6.c -o tunslip6 

flex-2.5.35
-----------
1. go to flex (project)/build/coretemplate/
cd ~/Digi/DigiEL-5.2/workspace/meconfig-ipv6-slip-jffs2/build/coretemplate/flex-2.5.35

2. configure:
 ./configure  --host=arm-linux --build=i386-linux --prefix=/home/<user>/Digi/DigiEL-5.7/usr
neu:
 ./configure  --host=arm-linux --build=i386-linux --prefix=/home/<user>/Digi/DigiEL-5.7/x-tools/arm-unknown-linux-uclibcgnueabi/arm-unknown-linux-uclibcgnueabi/sysroot

edit config.h:
/* Define to 1 if your system has a GNU libc compatible `malloc' function, and
   to 0 otherwise. */
#define HAVE_MALLOC 1

/* Define to rpl_malloc if the replacement function should be used. */
//#define malloc rpl_malloc //H.P.

/* Define to rpl_realloc if the replacement function should be used. */
//#define realloc rpl_realloc //HP

3. compile and install the lib type:
 make
 make install

libcoap
-------

2. configure:
/configure  --host=arm-linux --build=i386-linux --prefix=/home/<user>/Digi/DigiEL-5.2/usr

edit config.h:
/* Define to 1 if your system has a GNU libc compatible `malloc' function, and
   to 0 otherwise. */
#define HAVE_MALLOC 1

/* Define to rpl_malloc if the replacement function should be used. */
//#define malloc rpl_malloc //H.P.

add to makefiles:
CC = arm-linux-gcc

3. compile and install the lib type:
 make

bird
----
1. go to bird (project)/build/coretemplate/bird

git clone git://git.nic.cz/bird.git
patch -p1   < ../bird1.patch
patch -p1   < ../bird2.patch
autoconf

./configure  --host=arm-linux --build=i386-linux --prefix=/home/<user>/Digi/DigiEL-5.2/usr --enable-ipv6 --with-protocols=radv,rip  --disable-client


BIRD was configured with the following options:
        Source directory:       .
        Object directory:       obj
        Iproute2 directory:     /etc/iproute2
        System configuration:   ./sysdep/cf/linux-v6.h
        Debugging:              no
        Routing protocols:      radv rip
        Client:                 no

3. compile and install the lib type:
 make
 make install

strip fails make it self:
/home/<user>/Digi/DigiEL-5.2/usr/bin/strip bird


